title: Rapport (Chahyun)
description:
Description :
        Eunhyeon, an unmatched S-class psychic, he is also famous for having a glamorous relationship with the opposite sex.

He told him that he had a satisfying night with several guides.

It's not enough that I was suddenly assigned to a province.

In contrast to expectations due to the high matching rate Eun-hyun thinks that Jae-woo, who has become his new partner, is old-fashioned.

While he was waiting for the day he would return to the central center.

He witnesses a mysterious scene where Jae-woo gets along with a male Esper…
